      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im a personal trainer and i'm putting together some new group training programs. i want to make sure i'm being as efficient as possible with how i program for different ppl. are there any actual biological differences in stuff like muscle fiber types or athletic potential between different racial groups that i should keep in mind when grouping clients? just trying to optimize the workouts.",
